{"tid":791463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔中意動漫 打機 足球 同人少好多傾計投入感","createTime":"2018-08-23T21:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T22:32:19.000Z","uid":180913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4f5f891a542d19f25126f16057cb59db9a4fbc","tid":791463,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:42:31.000Z","msg":"特別打機<br />\n真係點打 都唔入迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好悶<br />\n<br />\n動漫就覺得幾靚嘅，但未至於 著迷<br />\n<br />\n足球日-悶，了解過，但連 世界盃 都唔會有投入嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n永遠 同枱食飯 唔識打機真係少好多話題，永遠都唔會明打機既盡興<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話題可能仲有，個種大家投入只有中意打機動漫足球既人會明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a4d70ec52244d1310c7435dd54690c27aa6797","tid":791463,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:43:59.000Z","msg":"咁你有乜興趣"},{"pid":"590d14ffd9696cf48571dbc1a2f89c2f178e89e2","tid":791463,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d5a4d70ec52244d1310c7435dd54690c27aa6797","tid":791463,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:43:59.000Z","msg":"咁你有乜興趣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:45:28.000Z","msg":"唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔講啦<br />\n反正唔中意呢3樣都夠死<br />\n係個種投入"},{"pid":"b8c5d23821f4c7991719e7031a2f5741add50fe1","tid":791463,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:46:45.000Z","msg":"咁電影，電視劇睇唔睇？"},{"pid":"503c59b22e3ef5d345c763f0d999d2abe47e9f2d","tid":791463,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c5d23821f4c7991719e7031a2f5741add50fe1","tid":791463,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:46:45.000Z","msg":"咁電影，電視劇睇唔睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:50:08.000Z","msg":"都睇既<br />\n但唔會好投入<br />\n就算連咩明星坐係我隔離<br />\n我都係係無反應<br />\n好似對咩都無強烈興趣<i